### List Available Tools

```json
{
"jsonrpc": "2.0",
"id": "1",
"method": "tools.list"
}
```

### Sample Tool Call

```json
{
"jsonrpc": "2.0",
"id": "2",
"method": "tools.call",
"params": {
  "tool": "${sampleOperationId}",
  "parameters": {
    // Add parameters here based on the tool's requirements
  }
}
}
```